    <div class="Article-header">
        <div class="container">
      <h1 class="u-entryTitle">‘I’m here for the money’ — My life as a Blackwater mercenary</h1>
      <p class="Article-excerpt">
  Wait. I need to feel bad about this. At least a little bad. Nope. These people don’t care about their country. I don’t either.
</p>
<p class="Article-author">
        <span class="Article-byLine">
      By
    </span>
          <a href="https://taskandpurpose.com/author/morgan-lerette-the-war-horse/" rel="author"
         class="fn">Morgan Lerette, The War Horse</a>
              |
      <span class="Article-dateTime">
    Published Oct 21, 2020 3:26 AM
  </span>
</p>
<ul class="Article-categories">
      <li>
      <a href="https://taskandpurpose.com/opinion/">
        Opinion
      </a>
    </li>
          </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
      <div class="SingleImage SingleImage--center SingleImage--hasCaption"><div class="SingleImage-wrapper"><img width="640" height="480" src="https://taskandpurpose.com/uploads/2020/11/morgan-lerette-stands-in-front-of-ishtar-gate-al-hilla-iraq.jpg?width=1440" class="SingleImage-image attachment-1069 size-1069 wp-post-image" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://taskandpurpose.com/uploads/2020/11/morgan-lerette-stands-in-front-of-ishtar-gate-al-hilla-iraq.jpg?width=1440 640w, https://taskandpurpose.com/uploads/2020/11/morgan-lerette-stands-in-front-of-ishtar-gate-al-hilla-iraq-300x225.jpg 300w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" /></div></div>    <div class="Article-body">
    <div class="Article-content">
      
